column1: Release tech preview 1
column27:
Steps to release TP1:
 * Tag [https://github.com/hyperledgendary/fabric-chaincode-wasm] with tp1 ✅
 * Publish hyperledgendary/fabric-chaincode-wasm:tp1 to docker hub ✅
 * Update [https://github.com/hyperledgendary/microfab/blob/master/Dockerfile#L56] to use the TP1 release ✅
 * Tag [https://github.com/hyperledgendary/microfab] with tp1 ✅
 * Publish hyperledgendary/microfab:tp1 to docker hub ✅
 * -Update doc in [https://github.com/hyperledgendary/fabric-contract-api-rust] to refer to TP1 images-
 * Tag [https://github.com/hyperledgendary/fabric-contract-api-rust] with tp1 ✅
 * Release TP1 version of [https://github.com/hyperledgendary/fabric-contract-api-rust] on crates.io ✅
